{"tid":1204106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚彈與胡椒噴霧 屬國際禁用化學武器","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T15:11:01.000Z","uid":221105,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f807dd2d848c90a391d9a0be68298e21210227d","tid":1204106,"uid":221105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"【惟工解密】參與佔領運動的香港市民或許不知道，警察向他們使用的催淚彈與胡椒噴霧是國際公約列為戰爭禁用的化學武器，不但在短時間內造成嚴重不適，更有可能帶來長期健康問題。惟工解密特地翻譯一篇討論兩者毒性的文章，讓參與抗爭的朋友有所提防。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n催淚彈及胡椒噴霧是《禁止化學武器公約》（Chemical Weapons Convention）禁止在戰爭中使用的武器。然而這條在1997年生效的國際公約當中有一條款允許國家向它們的真正威脅&mdash;&mdash;本國人民&mdash;&mdash;使用。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://wknews.org/node/570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwknews.org%2Fnode%2F570&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiVJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=312e2ac3\" target=\"_blank\">https://wknews.org/node/570</a>"},{"pid":"0f05533b61aeddf39d8e6ecb527fd0acfc06fe20","tid":1204106,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2840c39798056540b38ad3d454adb7b3d5825e8","tid":1204106,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f05533b61aeddf39d8e6ecb527fd0acfc06fe20","tid":1204106,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"如何提供資訊?"},{"pid":"bcf0542ada4b7d11de069a7a8c2e4718b5303384","tid":1204106,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2840c39798056540b38ad3d454adb7b3d5825e8","tid":1204106,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f05533b61aeddf39d8e6ecb527fd0acfc06fe20","tid":1204106,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"如何提供資訊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma